  <div tabindex="0" class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100 border-base-300 border">
    <div class="collapse-title font-semibold">What's a syncshell?</div>
    <div class="collapse-content">
      A syncshell allows <em>modded</em> players to sync their appearance to others within said syncshell seamlessly. You will need to set up Mare Synchronos and enter the syncshell details under the Join Syncshell button to be able to join the Limsan Lominsan syncshell. For more details on setting up Mare, please visit https://reniguide.carrd.co/#whatismare.
    </div>
  </div>
    <div tabindex="1" class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100 border-base-300 border">
    <div class="collapse-title font-semibold">How do I join the syncshell?</div>
    <div class="collapse-content">
      We have a handful of moderators that are online at various times throughout the day. You can ask for an invite by sending a tell to any of the moderators, though keep in mind that invites are at their discretion only. Currently, the moderators are:
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Lorelei Geist</li>
        <li>Hyper Mania</li>
        <li>Pq Tx</li>
        <li>Roro Chiro</li>
        <li>Maester Godspeed</li>
        <li>Hina</li>
        <li>Swassie Ojin</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
      <div tabindex="1" class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100 border-base-300 border">
    <div class="collapse-title font-semibold">Rules</div>
    <div class="collapse-content">
      By joining the syncshell, you agree to abide by the following rules:
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>No harassment or hate speech.</li>
        <li>Respect the privacy of others</li>
        <li>No spamming or advertising</li>
        <li>Follow the instructions of the moderators</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
